stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PendingVerification: Master signup
    PendingVerification --> Verified: Admin approves
    PendingVerification --> Rejected: Admin rejects
    Rejected --> PendingVerification: Resubmit
    Verified --> Suspended: Policy violation
    Suspended --> Verified: Appeal successful
    Suspended --> Banned: Severe violation
    Verified --> [*]: Account deleted
    Banned --> [*]: Permanent
